<h11>OWNERSHIP:</h11><br>
BOGGScoin will be given to <a href="http://boggsschool.org/">BOGGS SCHOOL</a> representatives at the <a href="http://reimaginingwork.org">reimaginingwork.org</a>. All initial transfers of genesis funds from Bitcoin or Doge will be done via public information technologies like twitter or bitcointalk.org.
